This paper proposes a method for generating images from scene graphs, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The method also involves designing a network to refine object crops, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed method's performance on datasets, which involves graphics (cs.GR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques.
